	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[3.63]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>The trival loot code was removed from the warrens about a year ago, all kobolds will drop everything they usually drop, now. Before, if you were too high, you'd get a message saying that you couldn't loot the item due to the level and it would pop. That isn't in effect anymore, which is why the hat dropped for you. It used to happen with molars to me. Now they drop whenever I'm in there.<br><br>People basically complained that the trivial loot code was flawed (and it was); so they removed it. Any level can do this quest, but a good level to be over is about 20-25 before trying, unless you're really really tough, or something. =)<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
